ook page we have created this code of conduct so everyone who participates can experience the same level of integrity views expressed on this facebook page are not necessarily the views of fundsmith its employees or its affiliates participating in or commenting on this facebook page constitutes acknowledgement and acceptance of the following code of conduct  we will not give specific investment or trading advice on this page and we do not endorse any comments or posts made by any person on this page  we do not provide customer services and nor do we enable financial transactions or answer questions about specific investments or your personal accounts through this page you should never post personal account or transaction information anywhere on this page  any personal data that you supply to us through this page is governed by our privacy policy which is at httpswwwfundsmithcoukprivacypolicyaspx  please do not post information or comments on investment advice or products specific securities or investments or trading strategies anywhere on this page  posting anything that could be seen as dishonest or untrue is highly discouraged and could result in being banned from this facebook page  all comments will be reviewed by fundsmith fundsmith reserves the right to review all comments and remove comments if they do not adhere to this code of conduct or otherwise as necessary  please allow us time to respond some of your questions will require feedback so it could take some time before we can provide an answer we will use all reasonable efforts to get back to you within  hours  do not post any personal information regarding others this includes addresses phone numbers emails or full names of anyone not voluntarily posting it themselves  you must not post the following type of posts on fundsmiths facebook page • insults verbal attacks or degrading statements • statements containing any profanity • statements that infringe laws eg encouraging people or instructing people how to commit crimes posts which are unsuitable for minors posts which infringe personal rights content which infringes copyright laws or data privacy of third parties • incitement to hatred racism obscenity • discriminatory or pornographic content • incorrect fraudulent misleading or other dubious content which does not foster a fair and open dialogue • spam or irrelevant comments which do not pertain to another posts on our page or another participant • commercial or private solicitations or offers for goods and services or improper use as an advertisement for websites or services or • content which contains viruses or trojan horses which links to damaging websites or which is otherwise capable of hampering the performance of this facebook page  be aware of copyrighted material we own the copyright and all other intellectual property rights in the content that we supply on our facebook page you hereby represent that you own the copyright and all other intellectual property rights in all content that you post on our page but you hereby grant a perpetual free licence to us to use that content you agree not to post any content on this page that infringes the intellectual property rights of others  links to other websites  fundsmith is not responsible for usergenerated content or for directindirect links to other websites if you notice any content that contravenes our facebook rules please contact us at enquiriesfundsmithcouk and tell us the offending content  this code of conduct is subject to change  fundsmith reserves the right to change this code of conduct at any time it is the responsibility of the users to review this code of conduct see moreawardswhat investment product of the month december categoriesfinance companystoryfundsmith is focused on delivering superior investment performance at a reasonable cost it was established to be different from its peers so as to achieve a different result in line with sir john templeton’s axiom that “if you want to have a better performance than the crowd you must do things differently from the crowd” the rigorous research process of fundsmith is central to what we do we apply exacting standards to potential investments to produce a portfolio of resilient businesses with excellent performance minimising the costs we incur on behalf of our customers in implementing our strategy also sits at the heart of our philosophy fundsmith was established in  by terry smith the business is owned and controlled by its partners who have worked closely together over many years and is headquartered in london with an office in connecticut usa it is structured to survive terry smith’s demise and continue with the same investment philosophy all partners of the firm have a significant coinvestment in the funds delivering a clear alignment of interest ancillary activities are outsourced to some of the worlds leading providers in order to deliver high quality operations whilst allowing the fundsmith team to focus on the investment analysis portfolio management and customer care fundsmith has valued relationships and manage investments on behalf of some of the world’s largest and most sophisticated wealth managers families private banks financial intermediaries and individuals wwwfundsmithcouk wwwfundsmitheu wwwfeetplccouk see moreplaceslondon united kingdomfundsmith llpaboutenglish usespañolfrançais franceالعربيةportuguês brasilitaliano한국어deutschहिन्दीmessengerfacebook litepeopleplacesgameslocationscelebritiesmarketplacegroupsrecipesmomentsinstagramaboutcreate adcreate pagedeveloperscareersprivacycookiesad choicestermssettingsactivity log facebook   fundsmithcom fundsmith is focused on delivering superior investment performance at a reasonable cost we apply exacting standards to potential investments to produce a portfolio of resilient businesses with excellent performance minimising the costs we incur on behalf of our customers in implementing our strategy also sits at the heart of our philosophy fundsmith eq